      "content": "thanks. i checked the staging area and the logs like u said, but everything looks okay on paper. the items are just... gone. like, no one logged them out and no damage was reported. it's just this weird, consistent loss of a few units every month. does anything else usually cause this kind of \"unexplained shrinkage\" in a warehouse setting?",
